articles.title: Kazakhstan is in turmoil and regional troops have been sent to quell unrest. Here's what you need to know - CNN
articles.description: Violent protests in Kazakhstan in recent days have seen the government resign and the declaration of a state of emergency as troops from a Russian-led military alliance head to the Central Asian country to help quell the unrest.
